<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>FOW Email</title>
</head>
<style>
    body {
        display: flex;
        justify-content: center;
        align-items: center;
    }

    .container {
        border: 3px solid #E5E4E4;
        border-radius: 30px;
        width: 290px;
        display: flex;
        flex-direction: column;
        justify-content: flex-start;
        align-items: center;
    }

    .img {
        width: 120px;
        height: 120px;
    }

    h1 {
        font-size: large;
        font-weight: 800;
        margin: 0;
        padding: 0;
    }

    .box {
        width: 250px;
        display: flex;
        flex-direction: column;
        margin: 20px 0;
    }

    p {
        font-size: small;
        margin: 4px 0;
        padding: 0;
    }

    .points {
        margin: 5px 0;
    }

    li {
        margin: 0;
        font-size: small;
    }

    .light-txt {
        color: #666666;
    }

    .down {
        margin-top: 10px;
    }

    .down > p {
        margin: 0;
    }

    .bottom {
        background-color: #F6FDF7;
        width: 100%;
        display: flex;
        flex-direction: column;
        justify-content: center;
        align-items: center;
        border-top: 3px solid #E5E4E4;
        border-end-end-radius: 30px;
        border-bottom-left-radius: 30px;
        padding-bottom: 10px;
    }

    .bottom > h1 {
        margin: 20px 0;
    }

    .bottom > p {
        margin-top: 15px;
        margin-bottom: 20px;
    }

    .link-box {
        width: 100%;
        display: flex;
        justify-content: center;
        align-items: center;
    }

    a {
        background-color: #5EC281;
        margin: 0 3px;
        width: 30px;
        border-radius: 10px;
        display: flex;
        justify-content: center;
        align-items: center;
    }

    .small-img {
        width: 100%;
        height: 100%;
    }

    .last-txt {
        font-size: x-small;
    }
    
    
</style>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <img src="https://storage.googleapis.com/fow-farm/fow.png" alt="" class="img"></img>
        <h1>Welcome to Fow!</h1>
        <div class="box">
            <p>Hello <%= firstName %></p>
            <p>Welcome to Feed Our World, the non-profit organization that puts food control in the hands of the people.</p>
            <p>Together, we can significantly reduce food waste, global hunger, and low incomes for producers</p>
            <p>As a <b>consumer</b>, you will be able to:</p>
            <ul class="points">
                <li>Connect directly with multiple local producers.</li>
                <li>Have detailed and reliable information about the food.</li>
                <li>Purchase the food in stock and on-demand.</li>
            </ul>
            <p>So, enjoy every experience and purpose within FOW!</p>
            <p>See you in the Dapp!</p>
            <p class="light-txt">Please do not reply to this email, as it is automatically generated.</p>
            <div class="down">
                <p>Best</p>
                <p>FOW Team</p>
            </div>

        </div>
        <div class="bottom">
            <h1>Feed Our World</h1>
            <div class="link-box">
                <a href="https://www.facebook.com/FeedOurWorld.IO" target="#">
                    <img src="https://storage.googleapis.com/fow-farm/Facebook.png" class="small-img"></img>
                </a>
                <a href="https://www.instagram.com/feedourworld.io/" target="#">
                    <img src="https://storage.googleapis.com/fow-farm/Instagram.png" class="small-img"></img>
                </a>
                <a href="https://twitter.com/FeedOurWorld1" target="#">
                    <img src="https://storage.googleapis.com/fow-farm/Twitter.png" class="small-img"></img>
                </a>
                <a href="https://www.linkedin.com/company/feed-our-world/" target="#">
                    <img src="https://storage.googleapis.com/fow-farm/Linkedin.png" class="small-img"></img>
                </a>
                <a href="https://www.youtube.com/@feedourworld./" target="#">
                    <img src="https://storage.googleapis.com/fow-farm/Youtube.png" class="small-img"></img>
                </a>
            </div>
            <p>2360 Hood Avenue, San Diego, CA, 92123</p>
            <p class="last-txt">You received this email because you registered on FOW.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>